ien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-xu%C3%A2n-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-3eXUWOuBCTV-7VojKdd_fw">Thương xuân kỳ 3 - 傷春其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/To%C3%A1n-vi%C3%AAn-t%E1%BB%B1-thu%E1%BA%ADt/poem-NBs0psuls_GOIHIBr9stGw">Toán viên tự thuật - 蒜園自述</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/author-l-NINz3JTJVTCX2aN0HlSQ">Thái Thuận</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi-%E1%BB%A8ng-V%E1%BA%ADt/T%E1%BB%91ng-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-th%E1%BB%8B-n%E1%BB%AF/poem-0qjrLatSCXpSwu2F0b6nIg">Tống Dương thị nữ - 送楊氏女</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi-%E1%BB%A8ng-V%E1%BA%ADt/author-XjaOXRT7NSnPjyRhhrtiSQ">Vi Ứng Vật</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-B%E1%BA%ADt/T%E1%BB%91ng-L%C3%A2m-Qu%E1%BA%BF-l%E1%BB%87nh-%C4%90%E1%BB%9Bi-Nh%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3c-N%E1%BA%A1p-xu%E1%BA%A5t-L%C4%A9nh/poem-sfPMF6rWawVmfFYBHwcQuQ">Tống Lâm Quế lệnh Đới Nhược Nạp xuất Lĩnh - 送臨桂令戴若納出嶺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-B%E1%BA%ADt/author-DkCT5T7YsHNTsWeoJ8uRqQ">Đào Bật</a>)<br></div>	</div>
